  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Jewels of Lake Maggiore is the perfect way to explore these stunning countries independently. Our suggested itinerary and optional extras which can be booked through our rep service give you the opportunity to discover the hidden gems of <a data-udi="umb://document/7b760653f95440289f984892a9c33c31" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b760653f95440289f984892a9c33c31}" title="Locarno">Locarno</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Maggiore</a> at your own pace. </p>
<p> </p>
